The next generation of binding and sumong for the sorcerer.  This spell<br>
like its lesser 'Ghost Chain', binds a subject.  This necromantic spell<br>
summons for a prison of bone.  It encages an unfortunate victim.  While<br>
the victim is still able to move, it reach is limited while that cage<br>
stands between the sorcerer and itself.<br>
